goals.active: The Ringmaster is going to hypnotize the Big Top audience!
goals.complete: I made my way to the carnival's big show and, as expected, the Ringmaster was preparing for his performance. It was a difficult battle, and the Ringmaster attempted to use brainwashed innocents against me, but in the end, I brought him to justice. Captain Thackeray offered me his sincere thanks for my part in continuing to protect the people of Divinity's Reach.

goals.active: You have received a summons from the Crown.
